org.eclipse.jetty.websocket.common.io

Class WriteCallbackWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.jetty.websocket.common.io.WriteCallbackWrapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Callback

    public class WriteCallbackWrapper
extends Object
implements Callback
    Wraps the exposed WriteCallback WebSocket API with a Jetty Callback.

    We don't expose the jetty Callback object to the webapp, as that makes things complicated for the WebAppContext's Classloader.
